    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You manifest a ravine of gravitational energy in a line originating from you that is 100 feet long and 5 feet wide. Each creature in that line must make a Constitution saving throw, taking [[/r 8d8]] force damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p><p>Each creature within 10 feet of the line but not in it must succeed on a Constitution saving throw or take [[/r 8d8]] force damage and be pulled toward the line until the creature is in its area.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><h3><span class=\"entry-title-inner\">At Higher Levels</span></h3><p>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 7th level or higher, the damage increases by [[/r 1d8]] for each slot level above 6th.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"><p><strong>Spell Lists.</strong> Wizard (Dunamancy: Graviturgy)</p></div></div><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"><p></p></div></div>",
